Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.05,0:00:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界因ZERO創造的奇跡而改變
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界因ZERO所展現的行動而重生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.14,0:00:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 當今世界正邁向新紀元
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.77,0:00:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伴隨著無數欲望與情感的波浪 ZERO必須前進
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.72,0:00:25.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是為了讓時針繼續前行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.27,0:00:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和約定的一樣 我一個人來了 到底怎麼回事 傑雷米亞君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.75,0:00:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說皇女殿下的消息只能告訴我一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.00,0:02:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,土之味
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.19,0:02:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑騎士團正朝著鹿兒島沿岸前進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.22,0:02:26.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是請大家放心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.68,0:02:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我布里塔尼亞在Knight of One瓦爾德施泰因卿的指揮下…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.78,0:02:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡已是布里塔尼亞的領土
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.97,0:02:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一兵一卒都別讓他登陸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人中計了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.31,0:02:44.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天英方向應該會薄弱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.47,0:02:45.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓登陸部隊咬上去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.99,0:02:48.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵軍朝著山口進發
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.03,0:02:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加西亞隊全滅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.47,0:02:52.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑騎士團這些傢伙 竟投入了這麼多戰力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.39,0:02:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算想維持國土絕對防衛線 東中華海戰卻一直被星刻壓著打
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.14,0:02:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要驚慌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要守住11區 以奧德修斯殿下為首的皇族都將入侵超合眾國
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其餘的Knight of Rounds也將全體奔赴前線
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.84,0:03:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是只要解放日本的話 布里塔尼亞的殖民地將一個個奮起反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.98,0:03:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界地圖將重新繪製
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.15,0:03:23.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.73,0:03:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是天王山
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:35.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經過去八年了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.45,0:03:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和娜娜莉被託付給這樞木神社
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.68,0:03:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.69,0:03:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 布里塔尼亞小子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.44,0:03:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:46.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次遇見了朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.95,0:03:50.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我救我想救的人 不需要什麼理由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久以前就是個不懂得變通的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是正因為如此 你成了我生平第一個朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.62,0:04:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 朱雀 我想賭在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.57,0:04:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假如你能夠接受我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.18,0:04:21.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不夠打啊 這種程度的祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:23.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亞的吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:24.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六角突貫陣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.37,0:04:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提問
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最珍貴的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.77,0:04:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.03,0:04:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 是生命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.40,0:04:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星刻大人 左翼崩壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.24,0:04:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一架突破能力超強的Knightmare
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.87,0:04:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓英迪拉隊去援護
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:05:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左翼全體保持後退 把那台機體孤立起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.37,0:05:00.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修奈澤爾皇子應該還留在東京
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.29,0:05:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼可擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.17,0:05:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九州那邊有帝國最強騎士Knight of One在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就留在東京 給他國一種「這只不過是場小紛爭」的印象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.86,0:05:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes Your Highness
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這場戰鬥很快就會結束
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假如我沒有判斷錯的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在長崎出現的伏兵 被Grausam Valkyrie隊消滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.53,0:05:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向島根派遣增援部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.53,0:05:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正面 也讓莫利卿去援護
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡利姆卿後撤 和拉斯科卿匯合重新編隊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人的攻勢看來快停了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.79,0:05:46.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦爾德施泰因大人出擊的話 一口氣解決他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.06,0:05:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.11,0:05:53.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太弱了 以ZERO的作戰而言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:05:55.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Galahad出發
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.39,0:05:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一特裝使用援護裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:05:57.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Galahad出發!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.62,0:06:05.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你說好了的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.55,0:06:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虧你能來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亞在特殊情況下 會設置31種路線
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:15.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中對關係到皇族的線路尤其鬆懈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.67,0:06:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你錯了 魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『虧你敢在我面前出現』
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是這意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:25.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是約定?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.17,0:06:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今誰還會相信你的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.31,0:06:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你為什麼也一個人來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.67,0:06:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.88,0:06:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我不想再撒謊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.99,0:06:41.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像對娜娜莉撒謊的你一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.78,0:06:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最差勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.21,0:06:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:48.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明一直背叛著我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.62,0:06:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對學生會的同伴 對娜娜莉也是 就連尤菲…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.84,0:06:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣好嗎 藤堂先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.84,0:07:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO的聯絡還沒有來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是Knight of Rounds都出現了 就算是星刻總司令也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:09.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.43,0:07:10.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼能夠相信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.97,0:07:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擅自跟Orange、羅洛之流同夥…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.23,0:07:16.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不覺得秘密太多了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.63,0:07:19.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這之前也秘密派遣木下他們…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.44,0:07:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO對目前的我們來說是必須的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.52,0:07:25.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是和扇他們說了很多次了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 日本解放以後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.68,0:07:29.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以後怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.81,0:07:36.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扇和迪特哈爾特去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不曉得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想威脅我做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.43,0:07:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威脅? 不不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想讓你作為黑騎士團的一員 一如既往的工作而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.99,0:07:49.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.35,0:07:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是希望你不要妨礙ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 能代替我的人有一大把…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:07:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因為你平凡 所以你的存在才有價值
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.89,0:08:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,組織這種東西 成員各個都很耀眼是不能維持的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想確認一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:18.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有沒有對尤菲使用GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你讓她屠殺日本人?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我下令的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼下達這種GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.06,0:08:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了讓日本人奮起反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日本行政特區成立的話 黑騎士團就崩潰了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.86,0:08:40.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏莉之死呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.07,0:08:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.59,0:08:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.18,0:08:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對你來說 夏莉和尤菲都只不過是實現野心的棋子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.41,0:08:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 所有的罪都在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 這和娜娜莉無關
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.19,0:08:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:08:59.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搬出娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.67,0:09:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 哥哥為了我 一直扮演著聖誕老人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:13.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫柔的哥哥的外表和ZERO的面具
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.54,0:09:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪個才是真正的魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.56,0:09:17.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 連這裡都沒來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀沒來這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.43,0:09:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.34,0:09:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把洪古的部隊投入左翼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.43,0:09:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備第二次突擊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閣下是指揮官吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.85,0:09:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擒王來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.56,0:09:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說是戰術的基本…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.63,0:09:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是Excalibur
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇帝親自命名的聖劍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.28,0:10:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我生平第一次向人低頭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.03,0:10:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顧不得體面了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:09.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除此以外我別無所求
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.98,0:10:11.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算GEASS也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.58,0:10:14.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 救救娜娜莉吧 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.73,0:10:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今…你這算啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.87,0:10:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以為你會被原諒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.94,0:10:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.25,0:10:24.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 現在我只能這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.26,0:10:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想救娜娜莉 只有靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你當我會原諒你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家會原諒你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.33,0:10:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你騙的人 因你而死的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:41.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有尤菲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:48.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今知道認錯的話 就把尤菲給我復活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.34,0:10:49.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.69,0:10:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用你的惡意挽救世界給我看看 現在立刻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是創造奇跡的ZERO吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有什麼奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:11:00.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都是計算和演出的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.33,0:11:02.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稱為ZERO的假面只是記號
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.75,0:11:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過是為了撒謊而製造的裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.15,0:11:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.87,0:11:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以為這種藉口能說得過去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.34,0:11:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是謊言的話 就給我圓謊到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是過去不會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有辦法重新來過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我 魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.46,0:11:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼給我下了「活下去」的GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.57,0:11:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.89,0:11:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對我下的「活下去」的GEASS 扭曲了我的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:40.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼對我下那樣的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.19,0:11:44.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我想活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:48.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我因涉嫌暗殺克洛維斯殿下而被問罪 你為什麼要救我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:50.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了獲取日本人的信任
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.83,0:11:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酒店劫持事件 營救學生會成員又是為了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想利用它讓黑騎士團亮相
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,0:12:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這眼神…我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是隱藏秘密接受懲罰的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:11.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我加入了布里塔尼亞軍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.07,0:12:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了補償 為了不讓悲劇重演
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.89,0:12:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是謊言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.88,0:12:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修 有一個補償你謊言的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.27,0:12:27.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是讓你的謊言成真
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.83,0:12:31.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你謊稱你是正義的夥伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.26,0:12:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就成為真正的正義的夥伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把謊言撒到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.49,0:12:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 要怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.93,0:12:46.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結束這場戰爭 如果你是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 這是只有ZERO才能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.44,0:12:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用讓世界變得和平 大家變得幸福的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.93,0:12:56.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼做的話 我就把娜娜莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.86,0:12:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救出來?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.97,0:13:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了娜娜莉 再一次與你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.02,0:13:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.46,0:13:10.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你的話 無論什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.93,0:13:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此為止了 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們已經知道你的真面目了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.84,0:13:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧 樞木卿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.66,0:13:22.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.39,0:13:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.56,0:13:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你從一開始就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.39,0:13:27.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.93,0:13:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你立下大功了 樞木卿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.49,0:13:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣戰爭就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 你又打算出賣我才…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:40.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你背叛我 朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.47,0:13:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你背叛了我!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.33,0:13:50.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為最近朱雀的樣子有點奇怪 就覺得他是不是有所鬆懈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.41,0:13:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是在學生會室發現的?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 當成寶貝似的放在儲物櫃裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.01,0:13:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多地方都被撕掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:14:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你… 和恐怖份子關係融洽的情形也許不太好留下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 大家一起麼就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.06,0:14:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是麼 那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.25,0:14:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也會流露出這樣的表情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從沒見過朱雀像這樣的笑過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.22,0:14:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.11,0:14:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:22.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是布里塔尼亞人和11區人的混血兒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.87,0:14:29.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放棄紅月 選擇斯坦菲爾德這名字的話 就可以很好的生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有這種想法的話 想成為Knight of Rounds也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.01,0:14:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是想問你有沒有回來這邊的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布蘭德利卿 請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.60,0:14:44.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被打成這樣 反正是要沉的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.27,0:14:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就讓盧西亞諾來有效利用一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.18,0:14:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一口氣解決
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.62,0:14:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然用同伴的艦艇來做武器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.54,0:14:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持炮擊 全速後退
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.28,0:14:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.92,0:15:00.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.87,0:15:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有兩下子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 在這個位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.75,0:15:14.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 挺身吃我一劍銜接隨後的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星刻此人 被稱為麒麟兒看來並非浪得虛名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:22.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星刻總司令好像負傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.14,0:15:24.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大龍膽 後退
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作戰指揮轉移給參謀長周香凜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.85,0:15:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒到時候嗎 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.15,0:15:34.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO的真面目居然真的是學生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.09,0:15:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉爾弗德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.84,0:15:38.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.49,0:15:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇族殺手ZERO的真面目居然是我的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是何等的悲劇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:47.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇兄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.14,0:15:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 魯魯修 皇帝陛下那邊由我來周旋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.50,0:15:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然 責罰是不可避免 你的性命我或許還能保住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:16:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想憐憫我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.13,0:16:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 全部是修奈澤爾殿下的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.01,0:16:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是跟著你就能找到ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.33,0:16:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下已經察覺到了 你和ZERO不尋常的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.53,0:16:24.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修 就算是現在我也想扮演你哥哥的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會害你 能信任我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.58,0:16:29.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信任你?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.01,0:16:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 信任你的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:35.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常遺憾 皇兄 我已經不再相信任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.86,0:16:38.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我的友情被出賣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.62,0:16:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉爾弗德卿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.40,0:16:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼人 你不是Orange
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 我只是想拜託你點事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.21,0:16:56.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了 要我做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:16:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼 很簡單的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.68,0:17:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當我擺出這個姿勢 那一刻你就把我當作科奈莉婭 然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.24,0:17:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科奈莉婭皇女殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.14,0:17:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的騎士吉爾弗德 救我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.50,0:17:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes Your Highness
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.91,0:17:19.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虧你注意到了 吉爾弗德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.42,0:17:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉爾弗德卿 你這是幹什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們才是 居然逮捕皇女 發瘋了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.28,0:17:28.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連吉爾弗德卿也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.49,0:17:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然只有相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.31,0:17:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇女殿下 暫且先離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.48,0:17:34.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:38.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了 我最初也是最後的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.48,0:17:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.63,0:17:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直無法相信 吉爾弗德卿居然會叛變
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.24,0:17:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.70,0:17:49.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡待機
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.39,0:17:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 修奈澤爾殿下的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.66,0:17:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說ZERO出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.93,0:17:57.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也沒被通知
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.29,0:18:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像得知什麼非常糟糕的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.40,0:18:02.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想確認一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.69,0:18:05.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有沒有對尤菲使用GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的話 應該清楚吉爾弗德卿叛變的理由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:15.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及你曾經在神根島採取的行動的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.47,0:18:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不是應該追擊ZERO嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.66,0:18:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們缺少非常重要的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.31,0:18:24.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所知道的情報…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.94,0:18:28.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wired-C 確認反應
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.85,0:18:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取得同步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.90,0:18:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ragnarok Backup 進行復位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.50,0:18:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉爾弗德 就這樣前往東京租界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.70,0:18:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes Your Highness
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.74,0:18:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樞木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.72,0:18:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.51,0:18:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日本人?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.70,0:18:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名譽布里塔尼亞人?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Knight of Seven
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.98,0:18:57.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是樞木玄武首相的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.73,0:18:59.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修的朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤菲米婭的騎士?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.45,0:19:09.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不願意說的話 我們就只有投身不公平的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.41,0:19:15.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想讓這悲哀的連鎖持續到何時
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,租界結構的修改已經完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.04,0:19:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會像以前那樣讓ZERO破壞這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.31,0:19:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捕捉到了 是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.29,0:19:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了嗎 蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.76,0:19:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備狙擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.42,0:19:29.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把Vincent打下來也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.53,0:19:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們以為我在租界就只是當個學生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.16,0:19:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東京租界 現在就讓你停止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.50,0:19:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.05,0:19:49.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.61,0:19:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Energy Filler…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.60,0:19:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gefion Disturber嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.36,0:19:55.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 關於這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.54,0:20:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,電視機前的各位觀眾 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.96,0:20:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,播放室的電源好像斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.28,0:20:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 條件就緒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.67,0:20:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤堂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.38,0:20:09.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.86,0:20:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七號作戰開始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.14,0:20:12.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斑鳩浮上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斑鳩浮上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.12,0:20:16.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艦隊各戰鬥部隊 隨時準備浮上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扇 現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.08,0:20:28.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本艦隊就這樣穿過東京灣 突入東京租界 和ZERO會合
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.15,0:20:30.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各員 戰鬥配置
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.09,0:20:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:33.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奪回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.41,0:20:38.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的忠義 為了魯魯修殿下和娜娜莉殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.77,0:20:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 黑騎士團突入東京灣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.37,0:20:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦爾德施泰因卿 派我和直屬的Grausam Valkyrie隊去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.25,0:20:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去東京租界嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.63,0:20:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼想建功嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.80,0:20:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我只是想破壞而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.61,0:20:57.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅洛 你那如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.46,0:20:59.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 作戰已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.10,0:21:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就去迎接娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.31,0:21:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 拜託了 羅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友情什麼的是靠不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.12,0:21:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜 無情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.47,0:21:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不將自我化為完全體 就不能把娜娜莉奪回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.16,0:21:24.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修 從克洛維斯那時我就覺得事有蹊蹺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.08,0:21:26.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 我已經理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.06,0:21:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我理解並接受了 現在所有的牌都在我的手中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:40.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 一開始就告訴修奈澤爾殿下的話 就不會引發這樣的戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是Knight of Rounds 我不能處罰你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.88,0:21:48.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心理的罪惡就自己去尋找答案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.38,0:21:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我該怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.46,0:21:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界不會只對你一個人溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.30,0:21:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有坐上去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.94,0:22:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐上這裝著Freyja的Lancelot
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.35,0:22:04.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用Freyja把魯魯修…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.48,0:23:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你真敢幹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.40,0:23:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,欺騙我 踐踏我的尊嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.41,0:23:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,鄙視我的人們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.10,0:23:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定會贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.62,0:23:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我會贏過修奈澤爾 朱雀給你們看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.79,0:23:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你們把我設為目標而行動著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.04,0:23:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 來迎接我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.61,0:23:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我來破壞 讓我給你們看看絕望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.02,0:24:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,然後我再去迎接娜娜莉 解救卡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.33,0:24:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,最後笑的會是我
